Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.89,0:00:31.50,Adashima - Default,,0,0,150,,{\i1}You see students skipping class on the rooftop\Nall the time in manga and stuff,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.50,0:00:36.27,Adashima - Default,,0,0,150,,{\i1}but if you actually took a nap up there,\Nyou'd get a sunburn like no other.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.04,0:00:42.02,Adashima - Default,,0,0,150,,{\i1}I think it's about time for\Neverybody else to start third period.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.60,0:00:44.93,Adashima - Default,,0,0,150,,{\i1}I've pretty much always skipped classes,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.93,0:00:47.68,Adashima - Default,,0,0,150,,{\i1}and Adachi rarely ever came to school.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.68,0:00:49.39,Adashima - Default,,0,0,150,,{\i1}We met up here by chance
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.39,0:00:52.18,Adashima - Default,,0,0,150,,{\i1}and ended up spending a lot of time together.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.85,0:00:56.03,Adashima - Default,,0,0,0,,Is it okay if I serve next?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.10,0:00:58.53,Adashima - Default,,0,0,0,,I guess...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.56,0:01:00.11,Adashima - Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.93,0:01:04.62,Adashima - Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.18,0:01:07.79,Adashima - Default,,0,0,0,,I looked that one up online last night.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.39,0:01:12.05,Adashima - Default,,0,0,0,,I don't have a racket at home though,\Nso I practiced with a rice paddle.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.65,0:01:16.05,Adashima - Default,,0,0,0,,No fair, you can't throw a curveball at a newbie!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.47,0:01:19.14,Adashima - Default,,0,0,0,,If {\i1}you{\i0} lack the drive to improve,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.14,0:01:20.97,Adashima - Default,,0,0,0,,that's not my... fault!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.56,0:01:28.73,Adashima - Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}When we're skipping class like this,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.14,0:01:32.73,Adashima - Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}we can usually sense if the other is here.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.14,0:01:32.73,Adashima - Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}I've only got like a ten percent success rate for now.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.10,0:01:35.56,Adashima - Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}So we usually come up and find each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.10,0:01:35.56,Adashima - Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}So you're getting worse...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.99,0:01:40.69,Adashima - Default,,0,0,0,,Let's do this!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.22,0:01:43.85,Adashima - Default,,0,0,0,,I guess third period was P.E.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.85,0:01:45.95,Adashima - Default,,0,0,0,,What if they come up here?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.10,0:01:50.00,Adashima - Default,,0,0,0,,Shall we open the windows and jump for it?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.00,0:01:51.96,Adashima - Default,,0,0,0,,What? We're two stories up!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.49,0:01:54.56,Adashima - Default,,0,0,0,,Wouldn't we break our legs?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.56,0:01:57.30,Adashima - Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, I see. So you're calcium-deficient.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.13,0:02:01.80,Adashima - Default,,0,0,0,,I dunno how you got {\i1}that{\i0} idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.18,0:02:11.04,Adashima - Default,,0,0,0,,Dang. This is kind of exciting.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.68,0:02:20.20,Adashima - Default,,0,0,0,,I don't think they realize we're up here, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.07,0:02:26.04,Adashima - Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe I'll drink some milk with my lunch today,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.08,0:02:29.79,Adashima - Default,,0,0,0,,so my legs don't break if we ever have to jump.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.84,0:02:36.80,Adashima - Default,,0,0,0,,I see — you've decided to strengthen your bones.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.76,0:02:43.18,Adashima - Default,,0,0,150,,Those moments where it was like nothing else mattered...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.18,0:02:45.01,Adashima - Default,,0,0,150,,always felt so nice.
