Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.83,0:04:31.37,Adashima - Default,,0,0,0,,Ugh, I can't anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.93,0:04:33.33,Adashima - Default,,0,0,0,,It's way too hot!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.33,0:04:35.04,Adashima - Default,,0,0,0,,Wanna go outside?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.04,0:04:37.00,Adashima - Default,,0,0,0,,It's almost lunch anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.35,0:04:41.09,Adashima - Default,,0,0,0,,My, how lewd.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.09,0:04:43.09,Adashima - Default,,0,0,0,,Our school's...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.09,0:04:45.09,Adashima - Default,,0,0,0,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.93,0:04:47.09,Adashima - Default,,0,0,0,,Dignity?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.55,0:04:50.03,Adashima - Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, that! Our school's dignity is at stake here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.60,0:04:54.60,Adashima - Default,,0,0,0,,So what are we doing for lunch?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.99,0:05:00.61,Adashima - Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, yeah. We can't have you go out in that state.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.22,0:05:03.22,Adashima - Default,,0,0,0,,Fine, I'll go.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.22,0:05:05.11,Adashima - Default,,0,0,0,,I'll go next time.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.45,0:05:10.12,Adashima - Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah right. That's what you say every time.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.75,0:05:16.12,Adashima - Default,,0,0,0,,Oh yeah, so I'll get you a danish, as per usual,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.25,0:05:18.88,Adashima - Default,,0,0,0,,but should I also get a milk today?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.81,0:05:21.13,Adashima - Default,,0,0,0,,Water, thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.13,0:05:22.63,Adashima - Default,,0,0,0,,Gotcha!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.55,0:05:24.72,Adashima - Default,,0,0,0,,Hup.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.51,0:05:29.76,Adashima - Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Being Adachi's partner in crime is pretty fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.76,0:05:32.31,Adashima - Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Is it because it's Adachi that I got hooked,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.31,0:05:36.60,Adashima - Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}or do I just get a rush from breaking the rules?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.60,0:05:37.90,Adashima - Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The answer's obvious, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.48,0:05:40.23,Adashima - Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Let's leave it up in the air for now.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.06,0:05:48.74,Adashima - Default,,0,0,0,,What's she even doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.01,0:05:54.00,Adashima - Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Shimamura was already here\Nwhen I first came up to the gym's second floor.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.66,0:05:58.87,Adashima - Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}She still looked like a middle schooler,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.87,0:06:02.75,Adashima - Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}so I figured she was a first-year like me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.89,0:06:06.51,Adashima - Default,,0,0,0,,A-Adachi, was it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.84,0:06:09.51,Adashima - Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.22,0:06:12.81,Adashima - Default,,0,0,0,,Um, we're in the same class.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.81,0:06:14.26,Adashima - Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, right.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.27,0:06:17.27,Adashima - Default,,0,0,0,,My friends call me by my surname, Shimamura.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.60,0:06:19.77,Adashima - Default,,0,0,0,,Like the clothing store?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.39,0:06:24.22,Adashima - Default,,0,0,0,,Do you come here often?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.22,0:06:26.19,Adashima - Default,,0,0,0,,I just happened to stop by today. You?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.56,0:06:28.99,Adashima - Default,,0,0,0,,Same here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.29,0:06:38.16,Adashima - Default,,0,0,0,,They're so loud.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.16,0:06:39.46,Adashima - Default,,0,0,0,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.81,0:06:50.55,Adashima - Default,,0,0,0,,Hi-yah!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.01,0:06:52.69,Adashima - Default,,0,0,0,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.39,0:07:00.76,Adashima - Default,,0,0,0,,You're gonna touch it?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.76,0:07:02.47,Adashima - Default,,0,0,0,,Cicadas aren't too bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.09,0:07:09.90,Adashima - Default,,0,0,0,,Think it'll stay?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.29,0:07:19.71,Adashima - Default,,0,0,0,,How many days do you think it has left?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.71,0:07:21.00,Adashima - Default,,0,0,0,,Dunno.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.00,0:07:21.99,Adashima - Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.85,0:07:27.25,Adashima - Default,,0,0,0,,How much longer do you want it to live?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.93,0:07:34.60,Adashima - Default,,0,0,0,,Fifteen days... give or take.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.56,0:07:37.93,Adashima - Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Fifteen days later,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.56,0:07:42.73,Adashima - Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Shimamura's hands were covered in dirt\Nwhen she came up to the second floor.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.44,0:07:46.69,Adashima - Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}And that's how she and I first met.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.69,0:07:47.67,Adashima - Default,,0,0,0,,Adachi!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.01,0:07:51.20,Adashima - Default,,0,0,0,,I got you the last danish.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.11,0:07:53.66,Adashima - Default,,0,0,0,,And here's your water.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.66,0:07:54.95,Adashima - Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.76,0:07:58.45,Adashima - Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Back then,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.31,0:08:02.19,Adashima - Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I didn't consider Shimamura my friend yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.74,0:08:25.60,Adashima - Default,,0,0,0,,Of course there's a book for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.60,0:08:26.56,Adashima - Default,,0,0,0,,Dang, that's expensive.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.18,0:08:28.60,Adashima - Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, it's Shimamura.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.72,0:08:30.89,Adashima - Default,,0,0,0,,Hino.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.89,0:08:32.45,Adashima - Default,,0,0,0,,Whatcha lookin' at?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.82,0:08:36.76,Adashima - Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Smash! You joining the table tennis club, Shimamura?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.10,0:08:37.64,Adashima - Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Hino is a classmate who's sort of a plain Jane.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.76,0:08:39.56,Adashima - Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}No, I was just curious.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.64,0:08:39.56,Adashima - Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}She's never dyed her hair,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.56,0:08:41.20,Adashima - Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}or even shoplifted.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.56,0:08:45.47,Adashima - Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Curious? You randomly picked\Na book about ping-pong?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.01,0:08:45.47,Adashima - Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}She's apparently never ended up in a catfight\Nwith a girl from another school, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.47,0:08:46.56,Adashima - Default,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.96,0:08:54.47,Adashima - Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Jeez, I was wondering where ran off to,\Nbut here you are chatting with Shimamura.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.06,0:08:53.26,Adashima - Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}This other classmate, Nagafuji,\Nis your usual glasses girl with big boobs.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.26,0:08:56.26,Adashima - Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That pretty much sums her up, I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.92,0:08:56.39,Adashima - Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}So what were you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.39,0:08:57.59,Adashima - Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Don't worry about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.26,0:09:00.06,Adashima - Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Her big boobs and her big attitude\Nmake her pretty mature...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.06,0:09:02.75,Adashima - Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}All right then, I won't.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.68,0:09:02.75,Adashima - Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}but she's a bit dense.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.26,0:09:08.06,Adashima - Default,,0,0,0,,Hino, do you have an excuse\Nfor that blatant sexual harassment?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.06,0:09:10.44,Adashima - Default,,0,0,0,,Nagafuji is too self-conscious,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.93,0:09:13.01,Adashima - Default,,0,0,0,,so I thought I'd lighten the mood.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.01,0:09:13.94,Adashima - Default,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.47,0:09:18.28,Adashima - Default,,0,0,0,,When they're this big, the boys are always staring.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.28,0:09:19.45,Adashima - Default,,0,0,0,,Of course I'm self-conscious.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.10,0:09:23.18,Adashima - Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure all the boys in class staring at your boobies
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.18,0:09:25.95,Adashima - Default,,0,0,0,,have fondled them at least ten times in their minds.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.71,0:09:30.17,Adashima - Default,,0,0,0,,That's super gross.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.17,0:09:32.81,Adashima - Default,,0,0,0,,That's the price of greatness, my lady.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.81,0:09:34.17,Adashima - Default,,0,0,0,,Whoops, my hand slipped.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.22,0:09:40.35,Adashima - Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Apparently, Hino and Nagafuji\Nhave been friends since they were little.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.35,0:09:43.26,Adashima - Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I only became friends with them in high school,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.26,0:09:45.90,Adashima - Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}so they're closer to each other than to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.52,0:09:49.18,Adashima - Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But when it comes to distance,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.18,0:09:52.40,Adashima - Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}it's not like being closer to someone is always better.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.03,0:09:57.11,Adashima - Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}If you get too close, you might fight\Nand have misunderstandings.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.70,0:10:02.76,Adashima - Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah. The other day at the fishing hole\Nthere was someone in a spacesuit...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.06,0:10:06.91,Adashima - Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, look over there!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.10,0:10:35.73,Adashima - Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I think relationships with others
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.36,0:10:38.00,Adashima - Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}are like free diving.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.47,0:11:16.28,Adashima - Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, who was that girl?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.28,0:11:18.78,Adashima - Default,,0,0,0,,Wasn't she in our class in, like, April?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.22,0:11:22.28,Adashima - Default,,0,0,0,,You say that like every time we see her.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.46,0:11:25.03,Adashima - Default,,0,0,0,,Her name is Adachi.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.51,0:11:26.85,Adashima - Default,,0,0,0,,She's our classmate.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.85,0:11:30.14,Adashima - Default,,0,0,0,,And she's a certified delinquent —\Nteacher-approved.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.14,0:11:31.56,Adashima - Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.56,0:11:33.14,Adashima - Default,,0,0,0,,Is she a friend of yours?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.14,0:11:34.39,Adashima - Default,,0,0,0,,Who knows?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.32,0:11:39.51,Adashima - Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}You keep sinking deeper and deeper,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.51,0:11:42.34,Adashima - Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}and things start disappearing around you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.97,0:11:47.51,Adashima - Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}You struggle to breathe, so you try\Nto get back to the water's surface.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.06,0:11:56.07,Adashima - Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}And then you poke your head out for some air
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.07,0:11:58.39,Adashima - Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}before sinking deeper yet again.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.27,0:12:01.95,Adashima - Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}If you keep repeating that cycle...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.43,0:12:12.62,Adashima - Default,,0,0,0,,Morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.10,0:12:19.63,Adashima - Default,,0,0,0,,Adachi...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.65,0:12:23.01,Adashima - Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, you're late today.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.01,0:12:24.38,Adashima - Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.19,0:12:27.43,Adashima - Default,,0,0,0,,I thought I'd just head home,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.43,0:12:31.14,Adashima - Default,,0,0,0,,but I heard a ping-pong ball bouncing.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.51,0:12:34.40,Adashima - Default,,0,0,0,,I saw you yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.85,0:12:36.61,Adashima - Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I guess you did.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.61,0:12:38.02,Adashima - Default,,0,0,0,,Where's your bag?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.02,0:12:39.90,Adashima - Default,,0,0,0,,Left it with my bike.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.35,0:12:41.72,Adashima - Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.79,0:12:51.27,Adashima - Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I'm heading home.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.81,0:12:53.91,Adashima - Default,,0,0,0,,Okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.75,0:13:00.06,Adashima - Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Adachi.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.06,0:13:06.81,Adashima - Default,,0,0,0,,"Let's go to class together today."\Nor "Let's walk home together today."
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.81,0:13:07.93,Adashima - Default,,0,0,0,,Which would you prefer?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.93,0:13:08.80,Adashima - Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.31,0:13:11.43,Adashima - Default,,0,0,0,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.35,0:13:19.73,Adashima - Default,,0,0,0,,Okay then. I'll just go kill time\Nsomewhere until school's over.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.06,0:13:24.86,Adashima - Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry for the wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.39,0:13:29.26,Adashima - Default,,0,0,0,,You didn't have to sit in the exact same position.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.43,0:13:32.12,Adashima - Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry you got caught in the rain.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.80,0:13:35.62,Adashima - Default,,0,0,0,,Well, it's not like you did a rain dance.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.25,0:13:38.16,Adashima - Default,,0,0,0,,So which way's your house?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.79,0:13:40.39,Adashima - Default,,0,0,0,,This way.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.39,0:13:41.87,Adashima - Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I thought so.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.97,0:13:43.89,Adashima - Default,,0,0,0,,Here, hold this.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.56,0:13:49.89,Adashima - Default,,0,0,0,,It's just that it's a pretty big detour from my house.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.89,0:13:51.14,Adashima - Default,,0,0,0,,I live that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.93,0:13:56.44,Adashima - Default,,0,0,0,,So whose place should we go home from?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.44,0:13:58.15,Adashima - Default,,0,0,0,,That's not a question you hear every day.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.01,0:14:02.65,Adashima - Default,,0,0,0,,Then... let's head to your place first.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.51,0:14:04.65,Adashima - Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.76,0:14:10.99,Adashima - Default,,0,0,0,,Riding double like this is against the law, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.99,0:14:13.20,Adashima - Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, and we're delinquents.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.20,0:14:14.95,Adashima - Default,,0,0,0,,Good point.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.95,0:14:17.72,Adashima - Default,,0,0,0,,Man, being delinquents rules.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.72,0:14:19.10,Adashima - Default,,0,0,0,,It sure does.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.39,0:14:27.01,Adashima - Default,,0,0,0,,I guess you {\i1}do{\i0} have friends, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.01,0:14:27.87,Adashima - Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.55,0:14:30.76,Adashima - Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, you mean Hino and Nagafuji?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.43,0:14:38.16,Adashima - Default,,0,0,0,,I thought you were always up there\Nbecause you were lonely.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.16,0:14:39.43,Adashima - Default,,0,0,0,,What about you, Adachi?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.43,0:14:40.48,Adashima - Default,,0,0,0,,Got any friends?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.98,0:14:44.98,Adashima - Default,,0,0,0,,Probably just you, really.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.35,0:14:50.29,Adashima - Default,,0,0,0,,Wow, that's sad!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.76,0:14:58.54,Adashima - Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Killing time outside of school\Nand then going home together is weird.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.54,0:15:00.00,Adashima - Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's definitely weird,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.69,0:15:05.00,Adashima - Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}but the idea of it is appealing and exciting.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.38,0:15:08.47,Adashima - Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}If either of us was an honour student, they'd say,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.47,0:15:10.01,Adashima - Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}"We shouldn't be doing this!"
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.01,0:15:11.22,Adashima - Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}...or something.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.22,0:15:14.76,Adashima - Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}They'd try to correct the other's ways\Nwith the power of friendship.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.31,0:15:19.76,Adashima - Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But we're both pretty irresponsible,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.76,0:15:22.48,Adashima - Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}so we're just dragging each other down deeper.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.27,0:15:29.56,Adashima - Default,,0,0,0,,I go through here, and then...\Nto get back to my house...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.56,0:15:31.43,Adashima - Default,,0,0,0,,That's a pretty decent walk.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.43,0:15:32.78,Adashima - Default,,0,0,0,,Shimamura!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.16,0:15:35.28,Adashima - Default,,0,0,0,,Here, I got you a towel.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.01,0:15:40.93,Adashima - Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.93,0:15:41.85,Adashima - Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.85,0:15:43.29,Adashima - Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? For what?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.72,0:15:46.79,Adashima - Default,,0,0,0,,For making you come all the way here.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.51,0:15:48.88,Adashima - Default,,0,0,0,,Want me to give you a ride home?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.06,0:15:52.55,Adashima - Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? That'd make the whole ride here pointless.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.35,0:15:54.79,Adashima - Default,,0,0,0,,I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.27,0:16:01.73,Adashima - Default,,0,0,0,,All right, I'm headed home.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.73,0:16:04.49,Adashima - Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I'll probably see you tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.10,0:16:09.86,Adashima - Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}When I looked down at Adachi's head\Nfrom the back of her bicycle,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.56,0:16:13.36,Adashima - Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I thought her hair, usually so pretty framing her face,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.14,0:16:16.36,Adashima - Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}looked like some kind of fluffy animal.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.99,0:16:19.11,Adashima - Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Maybe I'd look the same way.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.81,0:16:22.50,Adashima - Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What a weird day.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.51,0:16:40.30,Adashima - Default,,0,0,0,,See? I told you there were noises\Ncoming from upstairs.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.43,0:16:45.44,Adashima - Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? I guess you really were playing table tennis.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.85,0:16:46.94,Adashima - Default,,0,0,0,,Oh crap.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.35,0:16:50.28,Adashima - Default,,0,0,0,,Wow, way to make a friend feel valued.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.60,0:16:57.57,Adashima - Default,,0,0,0,,Shimamura...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.25,0:17:03.71,Adashima - Default,,0,0,0,,Adachi.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.75,0:17:06.63,Adashima - Default,,0,0,0,,So, how'd you know I was here?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.63,0:17:09.21,Adashima - Default,,0,0,0,,I remembered the table tennis\Nbook at the bookstore.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.21,0:17:10.46,Adashima - Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, shoot.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.80,0:17:14.21,Adashima - Default,,0,0,0,,So that's Adachi{**-san}, is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.76,0:17:18.97,Adashima - Default,,0,0,0,,I think that's pretty obvious, but yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.51,0:17:21.68,Adashima - Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, yes. Adachi{**-san}.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.68,0:17:22.98,Adashima - Default,,0,0,0,,You guys were friends?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.60,0:17:26.48,Adashima - Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I guess so.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.48,0:17:30.23,Adashima - Default,,0,0,0,,Then yesterday — well, whatever.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.06,0:17:32.39,Adashima - Default,,0,0,0,,I'm Nagafuji.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.39,0:17:33.24,Adashima - Default,,0,0,0,,I'm Hino.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.26,0:17:37.74,Adashima - Default,,0,0,0,,Nagafuji and Hino... Got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.60,0:17:39.60,Adashima - Default,,0,0,0,,Nice to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.60,0:17:41.74,Adashima - Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, I brought us some bread!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.64,0:17:46.04,Adashima - Default,,0,0,0,,I'm surprised they never caught you guys during PE.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.04,0:17:48.75,Adashima - Default,,0,0,0,,We stay pretty quiet whenever there's a gym class.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.59,0:17:52.25,Adashima - Default,,0,0,0,,Which one do you want, Adachi?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.05,0:17:55.26,Adashima - Default,,0,0,0,,Whatever you like is fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.51,0:17:59.60,Adashima - Default,,0,0,0,,Hm... Okay then, this one!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.76,0:18:04.89,Adashima - Default,,0,0,0,,Are you free on Sunday, Shimamura?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.89,0:18:06.64,Adashima - Default,,0,0,0,,This week? I think so.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.01,0:18:09.18,Adashima - Default,,0,0,0,,Wanna go to the fishing hole, then?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.18,0:18:12.65,Adashima - Default,,0,0,0,,That kid in the spacesuit\NI was telling you about is a riot.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.22,0:18:16.65,Adashima - Default,,0,0,0,,Aren't you just asking me to go fishing with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.99,0:18:19.53,Adashima - Default,,0,0,0,,No, no. That's just a bonus.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.53,0:18:22.98,Adashima - Default,,0,0,0,,They took a particular interest\Nin you when I brought you up.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.25,0:18:27.43,Adashima - Default,,0,0,0,,Why don't you just take Nagafuji with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.43,0:18:29.10,Adashima - Default,,0,0,0,,I have club stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.10,0:18:31.50,Adashima - Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.81,0:18:33.63,Adashima - Default,,0,0,0,,Sure, why not?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.63,0:18:35.01,Adashima - Default,,0,0,0,,Heck yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.01,0:18:38.01,Adashima - Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, we're going to the fishing hole on Sunday.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.36,0:18:43.01,Adashima - Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The next day, Adachi didn't turn up.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.60,0:18:48.89,Adashima - Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}There was a lot I didn't know about Adachi,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.69,0:18:52.65,Adashima - Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}and that frustrated me at times.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.65,0:18:54.82,Adashima - Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The only person I could understand even slightly...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.86,0:18:57.86,Adashima - Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}was myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.61,0:19:03.87,Adashima - Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}After seeing Hino and Nagafuji\Nhaving a blast up here yesterday,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.20,0:19:07.62,Adashima - Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I realized that was never what I wanted.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.00,0:19:13.68,Adashima - Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Adachi might not show up again for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.29,0:19:18.38,Adashima - Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Worst-case scenario, I might not\Nsee her again until graduation.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.31,0:19:20.39,Adashima - Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I might not...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.97,0:19:30.19,Adashima - Default,,0,0,0,,That {\i1}would{\i0} be the worst...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.19,0:19:31.44,Adashima - Default,,0,0,0,,not seeing Adachi.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.44,0:19:32.56,Adashima - Default,,0,0,0,,Blam!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.40,0:19:37.27,Adashima - Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.19,0:19:39.95,Adashima - Default,,0,0,0,,A-Adachi?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.89,0:19:42.03,Adashima - Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.61,0:19:45.37,Adashima - Default,,0,0,0,,I was planning to stop just short.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.37,0:19:47.18,Adashima - Default,,0,0,0,,But I couldn't brake in time.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.18,0:19:49.29,Adashima - Default,,0,0,0,,I'm pretty sure I heard you say "Blam!"
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.97,0:19:52.55,Adashima - Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, are you sure about this?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.55,0:19:53.50,Adashima - Default,,0,0,0,,About what?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.50,0:19:56.29,Adashima - Default,,0,0,0,,Well, your house isn't this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.29,0:19:57.97,Adashima - Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.97,0:19:59.51,Adashima - Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, you're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.30,0:20:04.47,Adashima - Default,,0,0,0,,Shimamura, here.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.47,0:20:07.26,Adashima - Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Wait, what?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.77,0:20:12.89,Adashima - Default,,0,0,0,,I was going to give them to you during lunch today.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.89,0:20:13.77,Adashima - Default,,0,0,0,,Lunch?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.15,0:20:15.97,Adashima - Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, so this is "next time".
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.97,0:20:20.28,Adashima - Default,,0,0,0,,I'm glad you weren't going home\Nwith your other friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.28,0:20:22.28,Adashima - Default,,0,0,0,,I wouldn't have been able to give them to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.22,0:20:29.24,Adashima - Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.24,0:20:30.28,Adashima - Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.83,0:20:35.46,Adashima - Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Adachi had said that I was her only friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.10,0:20:38.17,Adashima - Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}So I think I get the picture.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.84,0:20:40.81,Adashima - Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}This was about all I could ask,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.81,0:20:44.76,Adashima - Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}and this was all Adachi was able to say right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.26,0:20:47.26,Adashima - Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Adachi.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.31,0:20:50.56,Adashima - Default,,0,0,0,,You're walking me all the way home, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.76,0:20:56.06,Adashima - Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, that's the plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.57,0:21:06.99,Adashima - Default,,0,0,0,,Look at me! I'm a plane! Neaoow!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.61,0:21:13.29,Adashima - Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The slight elation that I felt\Nhad given me wings.
