Comment: 0,0:22:55.02,0:22:55.06,Adashima - Default,chptr,0,0,0,,{Outro}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.26,0:22:59.73,Adashima - Default,,0,0,0,,So what's Adachi{**-san} like, anyway?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.73,0:23:02.40,Adashima - Default,,0,0,0,,What's she like? Um, normal?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.40,0:23:05.53,Adashima - Default,,0,0,0,,That explains nothing, {*}Shima-moo{*Shimamu-chan}.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.06,0:23:09.58,Adashima - Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know how much I should tell you.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.36,0:23:14.78,Adashima - Default,,0,0,0,,Adachi likes water, preferably mineral water.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.66,0:23:18.29,Adashima - Default,,0,0,0,,It doesn't seem to matter which brand.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.29,0:23:21.54,Adashima - Default,,0,0,0,,I see. So Adachi{**-san} is a Namekian.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.92,0:23:25.68,Adashima - Default,,0,0,0,,I haven't seen her regrow\Nany limbs yet, though. Also...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.68,0:23:27.04,Adashima - Default,,0,0,0,,Anything biting?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.51,0:23:41.31,Adashima - Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The spacesuit stuck out\Nlike a blindingly white sore thumb.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.01,0:23:46.48,Adashima - Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8\i1}Suddenly, a small astronaut stood before me.
Comment: 0,0:23:49.90,0:23:49.94,Adashima - Default,chptr,0,0,0,,{Preview}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.65,0:23:52.45,Adashima - Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Adashimapedia: Ping-Pong!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.45,0:23:54.37,Adashima - Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Differentiate table tennis and ping-pong.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.37,0:23:56.74,Adashima - Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Ping-pong's for fun. Table tennis is serious business!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.74,0:23:57.70,Adashima - Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}So serious ping-pong?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.70,0:23:58.62,Adashima - Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}That's table tennis!
